name: Helevator
description: Helavator is actually a section in a map I’m working on called Too Easy. However, I thought I would make it a map in its own right as I thought it would be an interesting stand alone level. Interesting because of its unusual design and because it’s made in only ten sectors. I’ve read about the ten sector maps Doomworld compiled but too late to submit a WAD of my own. Still, I found the concept intriguing.
